<div class="bg-primary-light w-full min-h-[70vh] text-primary-dark">
    <%= render "shared/navbar" %>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto divide-y divide-primary-dark-300">
        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">Plus Ones</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    Due to venue capacity, we’re unfortunately unable to accommodate additional guests beyond those named on the invitation. Thank you so much for understanding.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">What will the weather be like?</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    Mid-October in Tuscany is typically mild and pleasant, with average daytime temperatures around 20–24°C (68–75°F) and cooler evenings around 10–14°C (50–57°F). Expect mostly sunny days, with the possibility of some rain or wind.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2" style="font-style: normal">Most events will take place outdoors, weather permitting. Backup plans are in place should conditions require moving indoors.</p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">Should I hire a car?</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    Renting a car can be a great option if you plan to explore Tuscany during your stay or are staying offsite. There is ample parking available at the venue.
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2" style="font-style: normal">For guests staying onsite we recommend comparing rental costs with shared airport transfers and coordinating with other guests where possible, all wedding events will take place across the venue so there may not be much need to drive during the long weekend.</p>
                <p class="mt-2" style="font-style: normal">Please note: guests with non-EU/UK driver’s licenses will need an International Driving Permit (IDP) to rent a car in Italy.</p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">Visas & Entry Requirements</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    For short tourist stays (under 90 days), U.S. passport holders do not currently need a visa to travel within most of Europe. However, an ETIAS travel authorization will be required for entry into the Schengen Area once implemented (expected in 2026).
                </p>
                <p class="mt-2" style="font-style: normal">Гражданам России потребуется оформить шенгенскую визу. Если вам понадобятся какие-либо подтверждающие документы для подачи заявления, пожалуйста, свяжитесь с Илья.</p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">What time should I arrive?</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    We recommend arriving by Friday afternoon to fully enjoy the weekend. The ceremony will take place on Saturday, October 17th.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group py-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between list-none">
                <h6 style="font-style: normal">What should I wear?</h6>
                <span
                    class="ml-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 text-2xl"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
            </summary>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <p style="font-style: normal">
                    Dress codes for each event can be found on the Event Schedule page. October evenings can be cool, so layering is encouraged.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>
    </div>
</div>